r />\n至少香港呢一刻又處於百年一次嘅歷史時刻<br />\n<br />\n若你 尚有感情<br />\n不如留低 伴我做見證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係諗住歸隱田園去澳洲耕田<br />\n見至連登仔真係好失望<br />\n推埋啲膠post<br />\n唔思考<br />\n唔用腦<br />\n成隻狗公咁見人就屌"},{"pid":"aab1e2a959423cac91ad6be96c8954005ba9ae15","tid":1900230,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"支那已經無恥到否認係肺炎源頭"},{"pid":"2a9ca862975350feb9f2d70dcfab5afd09765e17","tid":1900230,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"我只係想走，脫離呢個瘋狂嘅地方"},{"pid":"5fc89c0cefb6b7ad6a26ca6cfb9853eab03221be","tid":1900230,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"放心，支那已經自滅緊"},{"pid":"8456aecc5e8afe0a1a8f7f189b07b278f51aac77","tid":1900230,"uid":333471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:31:38.000Z","msg":"留條命睇支爆啦！"},{"pid":"e30b1658ea81d99db8ceaf15746ddb08b982a867","tid":1900230,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"The fact that the world is ugly keeps humanity beauty<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4556b1f00afba8d7703ee922b48b44af3e9354","tid":1900230,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"世界好快就會有大轉變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，詳情不講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ac1884866038d04b2ebc3f31316fd9102eec44","tid":1900230,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"死左只係去另一隻game,logout呢隻,login第二隻"},{"pid":"b8eda410fc7231a737edbd8f5587eac53cc46fd9","tid":1900230,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22cf9015858d52ca47ff862e19f21889b57b6366","tid":1900230,"uid":234961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8bf21edeac72