ets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"幾時先會有轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"好快會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb82c7a943beddc2da7f17e5756eaf025e249ef","tid":1900230,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"永遠都唔好覺得係最差<br />\n就可以揾到出路<br />\n唔好放棄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005717e763d32a5c98b82cf7833192bea5b0d3b5","tid":1900230,"uid":314604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:37:05.000Z","msg":"對抗極權從來都唔容易，我地一年時間都仲未有，要有心理準備唔會咁快睇到結果呀！<br />\n<br />\n我都會好灰，但諗起世界每個角落都有唔同人為理想為人類為地球努力抗爭甚至犧牲，我就唔想放棄，亦唔可以放棄。喺歷史入面所有人類文明嘅推進都係有無數人用好耐嘅時間先推動到，我地只係其中一個小小嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n如果對落番中共，所有人包括以前淨係掛住生活嘅我地都有份造就。我地香港人好大程度令中共變得今日咁強大，哩個都係一個共業⋯<br />\n<br />\n至於世界，冇錯我成日都有就哩世界末日嘅感覺。但如果睇番人類文明，你會發現平民嘅力量係越黎越大，要堅持先有希望呀！<br />\n<br />\n利申我唔係呀Q精神，我係悲觀地，但我真係唔想放棄。"},{"pid":"cc03a0f1267c0f02de26ad71125b1b2abe8c78ae","tid":1900230,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"日日睇住呢d新聞真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8f2eef1b3bccaf1d6ab537e5ef297ab719961d","tid":1900230,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"呢個病毒最緊要令支那滅亡<br />\n世界末日都無所謂"},{"pid":"ee5f2736219a45e313b7f43f9e53eb61d26f95ed","tid":1900230,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c8f2eef1b3bccaf1d6ab537e5ef297ab719961d","tid":1900230,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T09:08:50.